**CoinPal** is an exchange that accepts [[PayPal]] for customers relatively smallish order sizes and a weekly limit on purchases.

The site was first publicly available on December 31, 2010 (1.1).  On January 14th, 2010 CoinPal introduced an API that allows merchants and others seeking payment to use the service to accept micro-payments (1.2).

The operator of the site also operates [[CoinCard]] for [[selling_bitcoins]].

